    "description": "<ul><li><p><strong>Heritage (+2):</strong> Half-elves may express the grace of elves or human adaptability and ingenuity. A half-elf may either start with a free Edge of his choice or a d6 in Agility instead of a d4 (which also increases his Agility maximum to d12+1).</p></li><li><p><strong>Low Light Vision (+1):</strong> Half-elves ignore penalties for Dim and Dark Illumination (but not Pitch Darkness).</p></li><li><p><strong>Skilled (+1):</strong> Sharing the ingenuity of their human relatives as well as having slightly longer life spans, half-elves start with a d4 in any skill based on their experiences, education, training, or culture. If the chosen skill is a core skill, it starts at d6 and the skillâ€™s maximum increases to d12+1.</p></li></ul>",
